snippet.title: Only Fortress Online Game Trailer
snippet.description: The "Only Fortress" game uniqueness is that you are the hero of your fortress and you play the main role in PvP & PvM challenges! Bored from games where you have to watch how your troops are fighting? Not in "Only Fortress", here your skills and your tactics plays huge role in how You win the game!
